arts.ttl: Confirmed Lineups: Germany U21s vs. Bulgaria U21s
arts.sum: The team sheets for this evening's 2025 UEFA U21 European Championship qualification duel in Regensburg have been released.

arts.ttl: Leeds United man out until March with new injury timescale revealed by national manager
arts.sum: Leeds United midfielder Ilia Gruev is likely to be out of action for the club until around March after undergoing knee surgery. As attention turns to Sheffield United in seven days’ time, Leeds will be without their two defensive midfielders, and Ilia Gruev’s has proven to be much worse than Ethan Ampadu’s.
